<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>G</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 A thar lengmang, zing fatin, Bawipa velngeihnak
 Kan rawhral, lo nak zong hi, a zaangfahnak a si
 Cung ninu thlapa bangin, a tlang kan cungah
 A vel ngeihnak cu misual, kan damnak.

[C1]
   Kum a liam i, a thlum chinchin e
   Caan a sau i, a thaw chinchin e
   Bawipa duh dawtnak, a tthatnak kan caah
   Kum a liam i, a thlum, chinchin e.

[V2]
 Kan sual le kan, palh caan ah, a kan chimhrin tawn
 Bawipa nih, a kan hliam i, damnak a kan pek than
 Chim hrinnak, cu kan tthatnak, kan felnak a si
 Pathian fadawt, a ro cotu, kan si.

[V3]
 Thlarau i hruai, mi hna cu, Pathian fa kan si
 Rel cawk lo, in a thluachuah, ni fa tin, a kan pek
 A kan hnem, bei dongh caan ah, kan hmuh a mui dawk
 A orh lei kut cu, kan tthawnnak a si.</lyrics>
<title>A THAR LENGMANG ZING FATIN</title>
</song>